casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Seibers, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Seibers (1991), 60 Ohio St. 3d 62.]

(No. 90-2486 — Submitted May 6, 1991 — Decided May 29, 1991.)

This cause is reversed on authority of State v. McGlone (1991), 59 Ohio St. 3d 122, 570 N.E. 2d 1115, and State v. Cleary (1986), 22 Ohio St. 3d 198, 22 OBR 351, 490 N.E. 2d 574.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
